Sibonwe ngamadoda amabili abezivocavoca emgwaqweni, abe esemisa imoto ebidlula ahlaba umkhosi. Okhulumela inkampani yonogada bakwaReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe bafonelwe ngumnikazi wemoto emile ebazisa ngesidumbu esitholakele. “Onogada nabezimo eziphuthumayo kwaRusa bajutshwe endaweni yesehlo ngo-7.09 ekuseni. Bathole isidumbu sendoda eneminyaka elinganiselwa ku-20. Besinenxeba elophayo esiphundu,” kusho uBalram. UBalram uthe le ndoda ibingazikhombisi izimpawu zomuntu ophilayo, yabe isiqinisekiswa njengomuntu oshonele endaweni yesehlo. Uthe ayaziwa imbangela yokufa kwayo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, uthe kuvulwe icala lokubulala eliphenywa ngamaphoyisa aseVerulam. UColonel Mbele uthe izolo kutholwe isidumbu somuntu e-Oakford, eVerulam. “Ubenenxeba elivulekile esiphundu. Amaphoyisa ayaphenya ngalesi sehlo,” kusho uMbele.